column1: Baby Barnaby's////holy barnabys! this place is amazing for breakfast. Tucked away in an unassuming neighborhood
column2: Baby Barnabys is all substance. The coffe was great
column3: green eggs and ham was very flavorful. The boyfriend got a healthy plate and his egg whites were cooked perfectly. The chicken apple sausage on the side was the perfect compliment to the meal. I walked away belly bursting full yet i didnt have that guilty feeling of i just ate a greasy cow. All in all
column4: the food is really fresh and unpretentious. The line is pretty long sometimes but it is definitely worth the wait.
